    "preset_prompts": {
        "description": "预设提示词",
        "type": "list",
        "default": [
            "手办化 Create a premium, collectible 1/7 scale standalone figurine based on the image, meticulously replicating the character, made from smooth PVC and ABS plastic with a professional matte finish.",
            "动漫风格 {{user_text}}, anime style, masterpiece, best quality, high resolution, vivid colors, detailed background, digital art",
            "写实风格 {{user_text}}, photorealistic, hyperrealistic, 8k, best quality, realistic details, professional photography, natural lighting",
            "像素风格 {{user_text}}, pixel art, retro video game style, 16-bit, vibrant colors, crisp pixels, nostalgic atmosphere",
            "赛博朋克 {{user_text}}, cyberpunk style, neon lights, futuristic city, rain reflections, high contrast, cinematic lighting, 8k",
            "水彩风格 {{user_text}}, watercolor painting style, soft brush strokes, delicate colors, translucent washes, artistic masterpiece",
            "油画风格 {{user_text}}, oil painting style, rich textures, impasto brushwork, vibrant colors, classical art masterpiece",
            "3D渲染 {{user_text}}, 3D render, octane render, realistic materials, soft shadows, studio lighting, high detail, 8k",
            "科幻风格 {{user_text}}, sci-fi style, futuristic, advanced technology, space elements, blue and cyan tones, epic atmosphere",
            "风景插画 {{user_text}}, landscape illustration, beautiful scenery, detailed nature, atmospheric lighting, digital painting",
            "梦幻风格 {{user_text}}, dreamy style, soft focus, pastel colors, ethereal atmosphere, magical lighting, whimsical elements",
            "暗黑风格 {{user_text}}, dark fantasy style, dramatic lighting, high contrast, moody atmosphere, intricate details, gothic elements",
            "中国风 {{user_text}}, Chinese art style, traditional Chinese painting, ink wash style, elegant composition, cultural elements",
            "日系插画 {{user_text}}, Japanese illustration style, vibrant colors, cute characters, detailed background, anime influence",
            "极简风格 {{user_text}}, minimalist style, simple composition, clean lines, limited color palette, modern design",
            "蒸汽朋克 {{user_text}}, steampunk style, brass gears, Victorian era, mechanical elements, warm lighting, intricate details",
            "魔法风格 {{user_text}}, magical fantasy style, glowing particles, enchanted atmosphere, sparkles, ethereal light, mystical elements",
            "复古风格 {{user_text}}, vintage style, old film aesthetic, retro colors, film grain, nostalgic atmosphere",
            "恐怖风格 {{user_text}}, horror style, dark atmosphere, eerie lighting, unsettling composition, spooky elements",
            "治愈风格 {{user_text}}, cozy style, warm tones, soft lighting, comfortable atmosphere, cute elements, gentle mood"
